{"tid":1342643,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"劉細良：鄧炳強與元朗社團關係","createTime":"2019-07-21T17:48:20.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-23T12:41:05.000Z","uid":111253,"like":8,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"6613b4ab30f23ddd1605f5f6c236c9ec3ec9238a","tid":1342643,"uid":111253,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-21T17:48:20.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://thestandnews.com/politics/%E9%84%A7%E7%82%B3%E5%BC%B7%E8%88%87%E5%85%83%E6%9C%97%E7%A4%BE%E5%9C%98%E9%97%9C%E4%BF%82/?fbclid=IwAR0vkSleheNsQMD3Llf2i1tISZ8aWo5xDXkbrgWmKweK4__Htii8-vrfdfc#.XTSkZk7okOs.facebook\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fthestandnews.com%2Fpolitics%2F%25E9%2584%25A7%25E7%2582%25B3%25E5%25BC%25B7%25E8%2588%2587%25E5%2585%2583%25E6%259C%2597%25E7%25A4%25BE%25E5%259C%2598%25E9%2597%259C%25E4%25BF%2582%2F%3Ffbclid%3DIwAR0vkSleheNsQMD3Llf2i1tISZ8aWo5xDXkbrgWmKweK4__Htii8-vrfdfc%23.XTSkZk7okOs.facebook&d=Px13HBr2%2FanjjqouUL7W1Or6kk4zB%2BnGw4DSdwpbM%2Bg%3D&h=4c2c2dcd\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fthestandnews.com%2Fpolitics%2F%25E9%2584%25A7%25E7%2582%25B3%25E5%25BC%25B7%25E8%2588%2587%25E5%2585%2583%25E6%259C%2597%25E7%25A4%25BE%25E5%259C%2598%25E9%2597%259C%25E4%25BF%2582%2F%3Ffbclid%3DIwAR0vkSleheNsQMD3Llf2i1tISZ8aWo5xDXkbrgWmKweK4__Htii8-vrfdfc%23.XTSkZk7okOs.facebook&h=776f9fff\" target=\"_blank\">https://thestandnews.com/politics/%E9%84%A7%E7%82%B3%E5%BC%B7%E8%88%87%E5%85%83%E6%9C%97%E7%A4%BE%E5%9C%98%E9%97%9C%E4%BF%82/?fbclid=IwAR0vkSleheNsQMD3Llf2i1tISZ8aWo5xDXkbrgWmKweK4__Htii8-vrfdfc#.XTSkZk7okOs.facebook</a><br />\n<br />\n行動處副處長鄧炳強是現時對付示威者的最高負責人，製訂沸水政策在旺角丶上水及沙田圍捕示威者，造成大規模衝突。<br />\n<br />\n大家可能唔記得，他在梁振英上場後，2012年出任元朗警區指揮官，同當地社團黑幫稔熟，離任時梁志祥丶錦田鄧賀年歡送。元朗黑幫一直是梁振英支持者，當日在朗晴村諮詢會曾樹和及一班流氓便公然為梁保駕護航。<br />\n<br />\n今日元朗黑幫公然在車廂襲擊市民，昨天消息已經廣泛流傳，今晚八點白衫流氓通街行，區議員丶居民報警冇人理，元朗警方絕對知情，他們是配合黑幫襲擊恫嚇香港人。我們有理由懷疑，究竟曾任元朗指揮官的行動處處長是否就是主謀？"},{"pid":"6c5f31b39b95372deff94b5f9fb9dcc7c7a81bdf","tid":1342643,"uid":235345,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-21T17:50:11.000Z","msg":"壞link?"},{"pid":"8d962e5113601f3435c12eaa35a47989c3623325","tid":1342643,"uid":29080,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-23T12:41:05.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}